Ajit Agarkar has always been tipped to be the all-rounder that India

stories.title: India ride to victory on Agarkar's late blitz
stories.summary:
India coasted to a 39-run victory at the RMCCG ground in Rajkot to
close out the one-day series against Zimbabwe by four games to one
